data.description:
$5000 SELLER CONTRIBUTION with accepted offer!
This 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers a beautiful primary suite upstairs with a fireplace, a spacious walk-in closet, and a balcony with a view. Throughout the home, plantation shutters provide both style and functionality.
The gourmet kitchen, complete with an island, is ideal for cooking and entertaining. Outside, a large covered patio and a pool make for excellent outdoor living spaces.
Notably, the home is energy-efficient thanks to its solar panels.  They will be paid off at closing.
This residence combines comfort, style, and outdoor amenities, making it a desirable choice for those seeking a sophisticated living space.
